config.register_config(name='test1', config_type=bool, default=True,
    env_var='TEST1')
os.environ['TEST1'] = 'FALSE'
config.load_config_from_env()
assert type(config.test1) is bool and not config.test1
del os.environ['TEST1']
os.environ['TEST1'] = 'False'
config.load_config_from_env()
assert type(config.test1) is bool and not config.test1
del os.environ['TEST1']
